title: Student’s artwork selected for UW-Whitewater exhibit (University of Wisconsin - Stout)
text: ( Source : University of Wisconsin - Stout) October 16 , 2015 Artwork by a UW-Stout student will be part of an exhibit at UW-Whitewater 's Crossman Gallery beginning Monday, Oct. 19 , and running through Nov. 14. Kamie Hoover , of Rogers , Minn. ,
